# Styling System

This project uses a combination of:

## CSS Tools
- [Tailwind CSS](mdc:tailwind.config.cjs) - For utility-first styling
- [PostCSS](mdc:postcss.config.cjs) - For CSS processing
- Global styles in [src/style.css](mdc:src/style.css)

## Animation
- [@vueuse/motion](mdc:package.json) - For animations and transitions

## Style Practices
- Components use Vue's scoped styles for component-specific styling
- Tailwind utility classes for responsive design
- Custom CSS variables for theme consistency

When adding new styles, follow the existing patterns in the components and prefer using Tailwind classes when possible.
